high_descs: Take a couple steps forward, then turn right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spatula that is on the counter closest to the sink basin.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink basin, then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the spatula from the sink basin.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the microwave.
Place the spatula handle up on the counter where the microwave is in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the spatula from the back of the sink.
Hold the spatula, and take a step to the right.
Place the spatula in the right side of the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the spatula.
Turn to the right and go straight down, then right again to locate the microwave.
Place the spatula in front of the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a spatula and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the sink.
Pick the spatula up from the counter.
Go right and turn to face the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink and turn the water on and then turn it off and pick the spatula up from the sink.
Go right and turn to face the microwave.
Put the spatula down in front of the apple near the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula  on a table.
